  "detailed_description": "<h1>-ADD TO YOUR WISHLIST-</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502630/extras/309edb3b59ceb914f38d0a33ab45a111.avif?t=1766379227\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><strong>You can add to your wishlist and support us!</strong></p><br><h1>-IMPROVE YOUR STEAM PROFILE-</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502630/extras/4937df817c08694bd8fb259e5f889237.avif?t=1766379227\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>How about adding a touch to your Steam profile with colorful letters, numbers and symbols? After every level you pass in Neon Parkour different achievements await you! Profile development has never been easier!</p><br><h1>-SUPPORT US-</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502630/extras/fe250e4c77d054071267849603ee8d8d.avif?t=1766379227\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><strong>You can support us by buying the game for the bigger projects we will do in the future!</strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>In Neon Parkour, where you control a blue cube, make challenging tracks, overcome obstacles, solve small puzzles, don't touch the red cubes and reach to the other blue cube!",
